Subject: [PATCH 2/2] android: bridge devtools socket to localhost

---
 .../chrome/browser/DevToolsServer.java        | 160 +++++++++++++++++-
 chrome/browser/android/devtools_server.cc     |   1 -
 2 files changed, 158 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/chrome/android/java/src/org/chromium/chrome/browser/DevToolsServer.java b/chrome/android/java/src/org/chromium/chrome/browser/DevToolsServer.java
index 41a2e57377..312ff4fa5d 100644
